org.apache.commons.javaflow.bytecode.transformation.bcel.analyser
Class OperandStack

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.commons.javaflow.bytecode.transformation.bcel.analyser.OperandStack

public class OperandStack
extends Object

This class implements a stack used for symbolic JVM stack simulation. [It's used an an operand stack substitute.] Elements of this stack are org.apache.bcel.generic.Type objects. WARNING! These classes are a fork of the bcel verifier.
